{
    "manually_checked": false,
    "poem_title": "Miserias -- II",
    "author": "Juan Martínez Nacarino",
    "poem_alt_title": "Pero aquella mujer inimitable,",
    "corpus": "disco2_1",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": "1",
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "1",
                    "line_text": "Pero aquella mujer inimitable,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "2",
                    "line_text": "de inteligencia grande y poderosa,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "3",
                    "line_text": "justa, noble, pacífica, amorosa,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "4",
                    "line_text": "de conciencia cristiana insuperable;",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pero aquella mujer inimitable,\nde inteligencia grande y poderosa,\njusta, noble, pacífica, amorosa,\nde conciencia cristiana insuperable;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "2",
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "5",
                    "line_text": "mi Madre, en fin, la que encontró execrable",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "6",
                    "line_text": "la ingratitud y la llamaba odiosa,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "7",
                    "line_text": "¡te hizo siempre justicia, y orgullosa,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "8",
                    "line_text": "te quiso con ternura incomparable!",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++---+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "mi Madre, en fin, la que encontró execrable\nla ingratitud y la llamaba odiosa,\n¡te hizo siempre justicia, y orgullosa,\nte quiso con ternura incomparable!"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "3",
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "9",
                    "line_text": "Yo, ante esta ejecutoria, inmaculada",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "10",
                    "line_text": "por proceder de tan excelso origen,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "11",
                    "line_text": "y cuya validez se te ha negado,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-----+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Yo, ante esta ejecutoria, inmaculada\npor proceder de tan excelso origen,\ny cuya validez se te ha negado,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "4",
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "12",
                    "line_text": "siento aliviarse el alma acongojada",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+++---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "13",
                    "line_text": "de todos los pesares que la afligen",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+--++-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "14",
                    "line_text": "¡y doy gracias a Dios de haberte amado!",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+--+-++-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "siento aliviarse el alma acongojada\nde todos los pesares que la afligen\n¡y doy gracias a Dios de haberte amado!"
        }
    ]
}